<div class="section" style="background:#f5f8f1">
  <div class="screen-wrapper">
    <div class="caution screen" data-carousel-section="honesty">
      <div class="caution__bg-card caution__bg-card--left"></div>
      <div class="caution__bg-card caution__bg-card--right"></div>
      <div class="caution__slider">
        <button class="slider-btn slider-btn--prev" data-carousel="honesty" aria-label="前へ">
          <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 36 36" fill="none"><circle cx="18" cy="18" r="18" fill="#81C776"/><path d="M20.5 12L15 17.5L20.5 23" stroke="white" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="carousel-dots" data-carousel="honesty"></div>
        <button class="slider-btn slider-btn--next" data-carousel="honesty" aria-label="次へ">
          <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 36 36" fill="none"><circle cx="18" cy="18" r="18" fill="#81C776"/><path d="M15.5 12L21 17.5L15.5 23" stroke="white" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="caution__card main_01">
        <img class="caution__card-icon" src="/img/caution-icon-switch.svg" alt="" />
        <div class="caution__card-heading">切り替えは、ゆっくりと。</div>
        <div class="caution__card-text">今のフードに少しずつ混ぜながら、<br />1〜2週間かけて切り替えてください。<br />急な切り替えは、消化器官に<br />負担がかかることがあります。</div>
      </div>
      <div class="caution__card main_02">
        <img class="caution__card-icon" src="/img/caution-icon-bowl.svg" alt="" />
        <div class="caution__card-heading">合わないと感じたら、<br />無理に続けないで。</div>
        <div class="caution__card-text">愛犬の様子をよく観察しながら、<br />判断してください。<br />食いつきや体調の変化など、気になる<br />ことがあれば中止してください。</div>
      </div>
      <div class="caution__card main_03">
        <img class="caution__card-icon" src="/img/caution-icon-yen.svg" alt="" />
        <div class="caution__card-heading">まずは、お試し価格で。</div>
        <div class="caution__card-text">だから私たちは、2kgの通常パックを<br />お試し価格でご用意しました。<br />愛犬の反応を見てから、<br />続けるかどうかを決めてください。</div>
      </div>
      <div class="caution__header">
        <div class="caution__header-inner">
          <div class="caution__label">HONESTY</div>
          <h1 class="caution__title">わんちゃんに合わない場合は、ご使用をお控えください</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="caution__subtitle">
          <div class="caution__subtitle-text">すべての子に合うわけではありません。だからこそ、私たちからのお願いです。</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  /* ========================================
   * Base section & wrapper
   * ======================================== */
  .section {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    height: 100vh;
    height: 100dvh;
    min-height: 100vh;
    min-height: 100dvh;
    padding-bottom: 55px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    scroll-snap-align: start;
  }

  .screen-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* ========================================
   * Section root
   * ======================================== */
  .caution {
    position: relative;
    width: 440px !important;
    height: 959px !important;
    overflow: hidden !important;
    background-color: var(--background-03);
    will-change: transform;
  }

  /* ========================================
   * Background cards (left & right decorative)
   * ======================================== */
  .caution__bg-card {
    position: absolute;
    top: 355px;
    width: 326px;
    height: 326px;
    background-color: var(--white);
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 3px 3px 5px #0000000d;
  }

  .caution__bg-card--left {
    left: calc(50% - 509px);
  }

  .caution__bg-card--right {
    left: calc(50% + 188px);
  }

  /* ========================================
   * Slider controls
   * ======================================== */
  .caution__slider {
    position: absolute;
    top: 708px;
    left: 57px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    width: 326px;
  }

  /* ========================================
   * Cards (carousel items)
   * ======================================== */
  .caution__card {
    position: absolute;
    top: 355px;
    left: 57px;
    z-index: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 24px;
    width: 326px;
    height: 326px;
    padding: 0 18px;
    background-color: var(--white);
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 3px 3px 5px #0000000d;
  }

  .caution__card-icon {
    width: 72px;
    height: 72px;
  }

  .caution__card-heading {
    color: var(--black);
    font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .caution__card-text {
    width: 290px;
    color: var(--black);
    font-size: var(--font-size-m);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.45px;
    line-height: 23px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* ========================================
   * Header (label + title + subtitle)
   * ======================================== */
  .caution__header {
    position: absolute;
    top: 101px;
    left: 20px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 30px;
    width: 401px;
  }

  .caution__header-inner {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 9px;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .caution__label {
    align-self: stretch;
    color: var(--orange);
    font-size: var(--font-size-s);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.70px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .caution__title {
    align-self: stretch;
    color: var(--brown-title-text);
    font-size: 29px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.58px;
    line-height: 44px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .caution__subtitle {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    gap: 30px;
    width: 286px;
    height: 59px;
    padding: 0 3px;
  }

  .caution__subtitle-text {
    width: 286px;
    color: var(--brown-title-text);
    font-size: var(--font-size-m);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.75px;
    line-height: 30px;
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-color: #8F8376;
    text-decoration-thickness: 1.5px;
    text-underline-offset: 4px;
  }
</style>
